lead_paragraph: Russell Westbrook and the Oklahoma City Thunder could have been excused for looking ahead to a momentous visit to Golden State and a reunion with Kevin Durant looming Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Westbrook Gets 35, Leads Unbeaten Thunder Past Clips 85-83
headline.main: Westbrook Gets 35, Leads Unbeaten Thunder Past Clips 85-83
